Source: <a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/tiktok-shop-gross-merchandise-value-nearly-quadrupled-in-2024">Bloomberg, 2025</a>
TikTok Shop grew nearly 4x year over year. It is now the fastest-growing social commerce platform.</p>
<p><strong>60. The US social commerce market exceeded $100 billion in 2025.</strong>
Source: <a href="https://www.emarketer.com/content/us-social-commerce-2025">eMarketer, 2025</a>
Instagram Shopping and TikTok Shop drive the majority of US social commerce revenue.</p>
<p><strong>61. 40% of Gen Z consumers prefer to shop directly on social media platforms.</strong>
