Product tagging in posts and Reels drives discovery. Shoppable content earns 25% higher click-through than non-shoppable.</p>
<p><strong>63. 58% of social media users have made an impulse purchase from a social ad.</strong>
Source: <a href="https://sproutsocial.com/insights/social-media-statistics/">Sprout Social, 2026</a>
Social media shortens the purchase funnel. Discovery to purchase can happen in a single session.</p>
